      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone needing a dependable daily driver on a budget. The engine and transmission are both fully functional and have been regularly maintained, ensuring the car starts and runs smoothly every day. However, please note that the exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear and tear on the upholstery and floor mats. It has passed recent safety inspections and is ready for the road, offering a solid mechanical foundation despite the cosmetic imperfections.",
