    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a rewarding project? This car is looking for a new owner who isn't afraid to get their hands dirty! While it's currently in poor condition and requires mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast. It's a great chance to bring a classic back to life and truly make it your own!",
      "price": 6500.0,
