    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle offers a harmonious balance of performance and refinement. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it features a robust powertrain and a clean, well-appointed interior. Ideal for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience, this model delivers both sophisticated presence and proven durability. We invite you to experience the superior handling and exceptional value of this professionally vetted selection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape for its next owner! Everything runs smoothly, and it looks great inside and out. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver's car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example has been sorted for the long haul: the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to mitigate chassis fatigue. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. Performance is enhanced by a refreshed suspension utilizing Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in response. While the paint exhibits minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain is in excellent health, exhibiting strong oil pressure and linear power delivery across the entire RPM band. Recent valve adjustments and rod bearing inspections ensure this chassis is ready for the track or the canyon roads.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Well-maintained interior.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
